== Gameplay Notes ==
* Moon Idol Sea 1 usually cannot be caught with passive effects, such as the one provided by the [[Rod Of The Depths]] and [[Rod Of The Forgotten Fang]].
** The only exception is when catching a Moon Idol Sea 1 on the Megalodon Passive reel of the [[Rod Of The Forgotten Fang]], the Megalodon will instead dupe the Moon Idol Sea 1.

